 Public plan counters insurance company efforts to deny claims Ezra Klein. "Health Care Reform for Beginners: The Many Flavors of the Public Plan" Washington Post. June 8, 2009: "[Insurance industry] employs platoons of adjusters whose sole job is to get out of paying for needed health care services that members thought were covered."
